00:14:23.530 --> 00:14:24.420 align:middle line:10%
>> Wow.

00:14:24.420 --> 00:14:28.250 align:middle line:84%
>> And the James after he
met the emissaries of light.

00:14:28.250 --> 00:14:30.587 align:middle line:90%
How have you shifted?

00:14:30.587 --> 00:14:31.670 align:middle line:90%
>> That's a good question.

00:14:31.670 --> 00:14:34.520 align:middle line:90%


00:14:34.520 --> 00:14:40.610 align:middle line:84%
I think things have become
so much simpler for me.

00:14:40.610 --> 00:14:44.210 align:middle line:10%
I realized that this is not
so complicated, after all.

00:14:44.210 --> 00:14:47.330 align:middle line:10%
Waking up, enlightenment--
whatever you want to call it.

00:14:47.330 --> 00:14:49.840 align:middle line:10%
It's not this
complicated thing--

00:14:49.840 --> 00:14:53.010 align:middle line:10%
going to workshops, reading
every book under the sun,

00:14:53.010 --> 00:14:55.280 align:middle line:10%
like I thought, perhaps, it was.

00:14:55.280 --> 00:14:59.300 align:middle line:84%
I think I began to realize
that this is not something

00:14:59.300 --> 00:15:00.840 align:middle line:90%
that we have to do.

00:15:00.840 --> 00:15:02.810 align:middle line:84%
It's something that
we have to undo.

00:15:02.810 --> 00:15:04.970 align:middle line:84%
And when we allow
that to happen,

00:15:04.970 --> 00:15:06.770 align:middle line:90%
the process becomes very simple.

00:15:06.770 --> 00:15:11.400 align:middle line:84%
It's this constant stepping back
or surrender into the divine,

00:15:11.400 --> 00:15:15.360 align:middle line:84%
and I think for me, that has
been the major shift is--

00:15:15.360 --> 00:15:16.160 align:middle line:90%
>> Lovely.

00:15:16.160 --> 00:15:17.920 align:middle line:90%
>> Allowing that to happen.

00:15:17.920 --> 00:15:21.080 align:middle line:84%
And it's been a
wonderful process

00:15:21.080 --> 00:15:25.080 align:middle line:84%
because my life has
become so much brighter.

00:15:25.080 --> 00:15:27.080 align:middle line:84%
And I think the
other major thing

00:15:27.080 --> 00:15:29.630 align:middle line:84%
that I learned from
the emissaries--

00:15:29.630 --> 00:15:32.000 align:middle line:84%
and this is, I think,
really the culmination

00:15:32.000 --> 00:15:35.880 align:middle line:84%
of all spiritual practice--
if you want something,

00:15:35.880 --> 00:15:38.300 align:middle line:84%
then you have to
give that thing.

00:15:38.300 --> 00:15:40.670 align:middle line:84%
If I want peace, then
I have to give peace.

00:15:40.670 --> 00:15:44.630 align:middle line:84%
If I want only love, then
I must give only love.

00:15:44.630 --> 00:15:48.890 align:middle line:84%
And if we allow that to
be our simple guidepost,

00:15:48.890 --> 00:15:52.040 align:middle line:84%
then every moment gives
us a new opportunity

00:15:52.040 --> 00:15:53.930 align:middle line:90%
to express what we want--

00:15:53.930 --> 00:15:55.040 align:middle line:90%
to give what we want.

00:15:55.040 --> 00:15:55.520 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:15:55.520 --> 00:15:57.320 align:middle line:84%
>> Every person like you,
sitting here in front of me

00:15:57.320 --> 00:15:58.120 align:middle line:90%
now--

00:15:58.120 --> 00:16:01.290 align:middle line:84%
this is my opportunity to be in
heaven simply by seeing heaven

00:16:01.290 --> 00:16:02.450 align:middle line:90%
in you.

00:16:02.450 --> 00:16:06.950 align:middle line:84%
And when I do that, I suddenly
find myself just irresistibly

00:16:06.950 --> 00:16:08.640 align:middle line:90%
pulled into a new reality.

00:16:08.640 --> 00:16:09.440 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh yes.

00:16:09.440 --> 00:16:11.070 align:middle line:84%
>> Even though this
may not change.

00:16:11.070 --> 00:16:11.870 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:16:11.870 --> 00:16:12.410 align:middle line:90%
>> You know?

00:16:12.410 --> 00:16:13.580 align:middle line:90%
And yet sometimes, it does.

00:16:13.580 --> 00:16:14.020 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:16:14.020 --> 00:16:16.880 align:middle line:84%
>> But I suddenly find myself in
heaven, where a moment before,

00:16:16.880 --> 00:16:19.490 align:middle line:84%
perhaps I was in hell just
because I decided that I wanted

00:16:19.490 --> 00:16:21.380 align:middle line:90%
that and I gave it.

00:16:21.380 --> 00:16:23.330 align:middle line:84%
>> Who are the
emissaries of light?

00:16:23.330 --> 00:16:25.430 align:middle line:90%
How did you come upon them?

00:16:25.430 --> 00:16:28.730 align:middle line:84%
>> Well I'm actually just
beginning to realize, myself,

00:16:28.730 --> 00:16:29.570 align:middle line:90%
who they are.

00:16:29.570 --> 00:16:31.550 align:middle line:84%
For a very long
time, I didn't have

00:16:31.550 --> 00:16:32.820 align:middle line:90%
an answer to that question.

00:16:32.820 --> 00:16:35.870 align:middle line:10%
I just-- it was a very
mysterious thing, even to me.

00:16:35.870 --> 00:16:38.660 align:middle line:10%
The short version of the story,
in terms of how I met them,

00:16:38.660 --> 00:16:41.000 align:middle line:10%
was while I was in
Croatia and Bosnia

00:16:41.000 --> 00:16:43.850 align:middle line:10%
in 1995, I began to
hear these rumors

00:16:43.850 --> 00:16:47.013 align:middle line:10%
about this secret society
in the mountains somewhere,

00:16:47.013 --> 00:16:48.680 align:middle line:10%
but had no way of
knowing if it was true

00:16:48.680 --> 00:16:50.720 align:middle line:10%
or not until I
finally met a man who

00:16:50.720 --> 00:16:52.850 align:middle line:10%
claimed to be the
liaison between the world

00:16:52.850 --> 00:16:53.852 align:middle line:10%
and this community.

00:16:53.852 --> 00:16:55.310 align:middle line:84%
And he said that
this community had

00:16:55.310 --> 00:16:57.560 align:middle line:90%
existed for thousands of years.

00:16:57.560 --> 00:16:59.870 align:middle line:84%
Not the same people,
of course, but it

00:16:59.870 --> 00:17:03.680 align:middle line:84%
was almost like a lineage
of spiritual masters

00:17:03.680 --> 00:17:06.510 align:middle line:84%
that would always
be in total secrecy,

00:17:06.510 --> 00:17:09.504 align:middle line:84%
doing a very important and
very subtle type of prayer--

00:17:09.504 --> 00:17:13.819 align:middle line:84%
a meditation that they
felt would help all of us

00:17:13.819 --> 00:17:16.490 align:middle line:84%
to continue this evolution
into this world based

00:17:16.490 --> 00:17:19.250 align:middle line:84%
upon the laws of love,
like we said before.

00:17:19.250 --> 00:17:22.280 align:middle line:84%
And this person that I
met said that their role

00:17:22.280 --> 00:17:24.140 align:middle line:90%
was about to come to an end--

00:17:24.140 --> 00:17:28.099 align:middle line:84%
that the community was
about to disband because--

00:17:28.099 --> 00:17:32.120 align:middle line:84%
almost as if us,
as an adolescent,

00:17:32.120 --> 00:17:35.750 align:middle line:84%
had become an adult. And
when one becomes an adult,

00:17:35.750 --> 00:17:37.745 align:middle line:90%
the guardian steps back.

00:17:37.745 --> 00:17:40.370 align:middle line:84%
And that is essentially what was
happening with the emissaries.

00:17:40.370 --> 00:17:44.250 align:middle line:84%
We're ready now to be
giving this same light--

00:17:44.250 --> 00:17:47.180 align:middle line:84%
the same gift that they had been
giving to us-- to each other.

00:17:47.180 --> 00:17:49.280 align:middle line:84%
>> Do you have a sense
of why you were picked?

00:17:49.280 --> 00:17:50.270 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, I do.

00:17:50.270 --> 00:17:52.050 align:middle line:84%
It took a while
for me to get it.

00:17:52.050 --> 00:17:54.035 align:middle line:90%
At first, when I was there--

00:17:54.035 --> 00:17:56.400 align:middle line:84%
or when I got back, really,
it was like, why me?

00:17:56.400 --> 00:17:57.200 align:middle line:90%
>> Sure.

00:17:57.200 --> 00:17:58.140 align:middle line:90%
>> Who am I?

00:17:58.140 --> 00:17:59.515 align:middle line:84%
And then after
about three months

00:17:59.515 --> 00:18:01.970 align:middle line:84%
of wandering around, asking
that question, it hit me.

00:18:01.970 --> 00:18:05.793 align:middle line:84%
And I think that the reason why
it was me is very important.

00:18:05.793 --> 00:18:08.210 align:middle line:84%
The reason why I was the one
brought up into the mountains

00:18:08.210 --> 00:18:11.810 align:middle line:84%
to be with these emissaries--
to be given this incredible

00:18:11.810 --> 00:18:12.980 align:middle line:90%
message--

00:18:12.980 --> 00:18:19.460 align:middle line:84%
is simply because I am no
different than anybody else.

00:18:19.460 --> 00:18:21.920 align:middle line:84%
Now that may sound like a
very silly, simple reason,

00:18:21.920 --> 00:18:24.290 align:middle line:84%
but the fact is
it's very profound.

00:18:24.290 --> 00:18:27.580 align:middle line:84%
Someone that was this
master wasn't drawn up.

00:18:27.580 --> 00:18:29.690 align:middle line:84%
Someone who-- a world
leader-- it wasn't someone

00:18:29.690 --> 00:18:32.240 align:middle line:84%
like that because so
often, we pick teachers

00:18:32.240 --> 00:18:34.153 align:middle line:84%
of people who are
different from us,

00:18:34.153 --> 00:18:36.570 align:middle line:84%
like someone from a different
country, different language,

00:18:36.570 --> 00:18:37.790 align:middle line:90%
different religion.

00:18:37.790 --> 00:18:40.890 align:middle line:84%
It makes it easy for us to
say, well, it's easy for you,

00:18:40.890 --> 00:18:42.240 align:middle line:90%
but look how different I am.

00:18:42.240 --> 00:18:43.040 align:middle line:90%
Well guess what?

00:18:43.040 --> 00:18:44.900 align:middle line:84%
I'm not different
than other people.

00:18:44.900 --> 00:18:46.720 align:middle line:90%
I'm very ordinary.

00:18:46.720 --> 00:18:48.980 align:middle line:84%
And the fact that
I was the one that

00:18:48.980 --> 00:18:51.200 align:middle line:84%
was brought up
there, I believe, was

00:18:51.200 --> 00:18:52.460 align:middle line:90%
because this is for all of us.

00:18:52.460 --> 00:18:55.040 align:middle line:84%
It has nothing to do with
being extraordinary anymore.

00:18:55.040 --> 00:18:57.560 align:middle line:84%
This has to do with each one
of us realizing that even

00:18:57.560 --> 00:18:59.195 align:middle line:84%
in my ordinariness,
I'm extraordinary.

00:18:59.195 --> 00:19:00.140 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:19:00.140 --> 00:19:03.800 align:middle line:84%
And do you find now that
you have this that projects

00:19:03.800 --> 00:19:05.430 align:middle line:90%
are put in front of you?

00:19:05.430 --> 00:19:07.710 align:middle line:84%
And do you know what
you have to do next?

00:19:07.710 --> 00:19:09.320 align:middle line:84%
What's the next
project that's been

00:19:09.320 --> 00:19:12.770 align:middle line:84%
placed in front of James that
says, here's where you go next?

00:19:12.770 --> 00:19:14.780 align:middle line:84%
You just show up
and say, present.

00:19:14.780 --> 00:19:16.930 align:middle line:84%
>> Yeah, that seems to
be the way it happens.

00:19:16.930 --> 00:19:18.890 align:middle line:90%
I certainly can't--

00:19:18.890 --> 00:19:20.930 align:middle line:90%
I can't come up with it myself.

00:19:20.930 --> 00:19:22.670 align:middle line:10%
The thing that seems
to be happening now

00:19:22.670 --> 00:19:26.150 align:middle line:10%
as we approach the dawn
of a new millennium

00:19:26.150 --> 00:19:28.700 align:middle line:10%
is we're starting a
project called the Cloth

00:19:28.700 --> 00:19:30.500 align:middle line:10%
of Many Colors
Peace Project, where

00:19:30.500 --> 00:19:33.170 align:middle line:10%
we're going to be asking
5 million people, which

00:19:33.170 --> 00:19:39.050 align:middle line:10%
is about 1/10 of 1% of the whole
population of the planet Earth,

00:19:39.050 --> 00:19:42.290 align:middle line:10%
to cut off a piece of cloth
off a piece of clothing,

00:19:42.290 --> 00:19:45.230 align:middle line:10%
hold that piece of
cloth, and feel--

00:19:45.230 --> 00:19:46.490 align:middle line:10%
like charge it with peace.

00:19:46.490 --> 00:19:47.802 align:middle line:90%
And all those cloths--

00:19:47.802 --> 00:19:49.760 align:middle line:84%
pieces of cloth-- are
going to be sewn together

00:19:49.760 --> 00:19:53.110 align:middle line:84%
into an enormous banner,
that on January 1 of 2000

00:19:53.110 --> 00:19:55.610 align:middle line:84%
is going to be wrapped around
the base of the United Nations

00:19:55.610 --> 00:19:57.500 align:middle line:90%
building in New York.

00:19:57.500 --> 00:19:59.900 align:middle line:84%
And then what we're going
to do with that cloth

00:19:59.900 --> 00:20:03.140 align:middle line:84%
